<div class="legend"><span class="legend-color" style="display:inline-block; width:1.5em; height:1.5em; margin:1px 0; border:1px solid black; background-color: #8A8B8D; color:black; font-size:100%; text-align:center;">&#160;</span>&#160;other languages</div>
